# howard wang

senior at swarthmore college studying engineering and applied mathematics.  
research interests in computational neuroscience, biomedical engineering, and applied mathematics.  

---

## current work
- developing pde-based models of t-cell dynamics in lymph node microenvironments  
- building pipelines for 3d analysis of jaw and mouth motion in nonhuman primates for neuromechanics and brain–computer interfaces  
- eeg analysis, emi data analytics, and neuromorphic hardware implementations  

